{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/h9rIWt5A7iA1WuM8IPv6VsQMRCy.jpg","belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":18,"name":"Drama"}],"homepage":"","id":1168719,"imdb_id":"tt27811632","origin_country":["FR","DE","HU"],"original_language":"de","original_title":"Silent Friend","overview":"On the grounds of a medieval German university town looms an imposing Ginkgo biloba, a tree whose longevity stands in marked contrast to three intimate, human-scaled stories. In 1908, the university’s first female student gains admission into the prestigious botany department, confronting the sexism of both professors and peers. In 1972, amidst counterculture movements, a reserved student finds his attention captured by a fellow housemate and the geranium plant she studies. In 2020, during the COVID-19 pandemic, a neuroscientist from Hong Kong secures the help of a renowned botanist for an experiment on the old ginkgo tree.","popularity":7.9902,"poster_path":"/r52BdT1QKYBbJv6OJfqJCAdDqfh.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":140,"logo_path":"/ooz5b0ov3PLfBoOJyMmdoffVuHs.png","name":"Pandora Film","origin_country":"DE"},{"id":793,"logo_path":"/10DhIXAmAixQvBOsjZ1MOeSRyUC.png","name":"Galatée Films","origin_country":"FR"},{"id":11008,"logo_path":"/ygmbJsCJjgzIIYrJSj9grhDCYFu.png","name":"Inforg-M&M Film","origin_country":"HU"},{"id":127914,"logo_path":"/xaPfwbAnv2ULcCil5x6dPFmFs8z.png","name":"Rediance","origin_country":"CN"},{"id":11237,"logo_path":"/nzPEges9ftjCDQWru0qrIfTX8OR.png","name":"ZDF/Arte","origin_country":"DE"},{"id":94,"logo_path":"/huC7HqorvUThGIrENrbcHmQVUA0.png","name":"ARTE France Cinéma","origin_country":"FR"},{"id":274902,"logo_path":null,"name":"Allons Voir","origin_country":"BE"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"FR","name":"France"},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","name":"Germany"},{"iso_3166_1":"HU","name":"Hungary"},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","name":"China"},{"iso_3166_1":"BE","name":"Belgium"}],"release_date":"2026-01-15","revenue":582186,"runtime":147,"softcore":false,